{"tid":1589184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃秋生撐被捕學生：兩張八達通涉盜竊? 兩個銀行户口咪打劫銀行？","createTime":"2019-09-23T07:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T03:38:36.000Z","uid":54373,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"498e851e2ab10099986c8feba38990197ee30a72","tid":1589184,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:21:40.000Z","msg":"影帝黃秋生一向都關心時事，之前告別Facebook，轉玩Twitter，仍喺網上繼續發表意見。<br />\n<br />\n對於有人因為持兩張八達通涉盜竊被捕，秋生則指：「兩個銀行户口咪打劫銀行？」<br />\n<br />\n琴日各區均有示威活動，警方喺城門隧道設置路障截查可疑人士。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名15歲少年嘅銀包中有兩張八達通，警方懷疑八達通唔屬於事主，係屬於其他人，涉嫌盜竊拘捕嗰位少年。<br />\n<br />\n黃秋生亦都share咗一個蒙面黑衣女子以警棍截查示威者嘅新聞，留言指：「駛乜有証，最緊要有警棍。人人都係警察」"},{"pid":"5e4ed70decb21a8d75aa8a3f764942f21f4c7858","tid":1589184,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"e2e17c4e8e827c81f5b28349fbfc27b3eb8d89cd","tid":1589184,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756891df52aab418feb251c23074aa3b4bff0d28","tid":1589184,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:38:10.000Z","msg":"而家香港就係咁荒謬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a076aa7e9463175f57c0b71f30d7784515c03d","tid":1589184,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:38:36.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" cl